Packed with photos, in-depth interviews and news focused on pop culture at large, PEOPLE magazine is a valuable source to finding out what's happening in Hollywood and cultural trends affecting Americans today. PEOPLE magazine also reports on a variety of subjects beyond celebrities like books, fashion, movies and nationwide events. PEOPLE magazine is best known for its annual publication of its "100 Most Beautiful People" issue. Other special annual issues include "The Sexiest Man Alive" and "The Best and Worst Dressed Celebrities."
